snippet.title: BEFIKAR | Tanzeel Khan ft. Aashna Hegde
snippet.description:
GIVING YOU GUYS A PART OF OUR HEARTS WITH [ B E F I K A R ] üë´‚ô•Ô∏è

This song depicts young love, love that has no bounds! A song that‚Äôll make you feel all the emotions, that‚Äôll make you dance your heart away! So go enjoy this song with your loved ones, tell them you love them and always remember to love without any fikar, love Befikar!

#Befikar #TanzeelKhan #AashnaHegde

______________________________________
Audio
Artists : Tanzeel Khan & Aashna Hegde
Lyrics & Composition : Tanzeel Khan
Music : Akarsh Shetty
Mixing & Mastering : Hanish Taneja

Video
Director : Vaibhav Patil
Artist Manager/Line Producer : Dane Pereira
Production Manager : Ashish Guria
DOPs : Arun Sharma, Appu VS
Edit : Shubham Vasudev
Colour Grading & Sound Correction : Abhishek Kini
Crew : Aakash Chepya
MUA: Kausha Lodaliya

Location : Big Mama

______________________________________
Lyrics:

[Tanzeel]
Mera dil Meri jaaan
Mujhse na chupa
Chahat karde bayaaan
Mere dil ka kya? 

Dil mein hai baatein meri jo basi voh
Keh na saka mein tumse kabhi jo
Dena hai dil ab bas yeh tum hi ko
Chahat meri ab se tum hi ho

Kaise bhula du saari voh baatein
Khush bhi hu toh tere sahaare
Soye na ab hum kitni hi raatein
Paya hai tujko ab yeh jahan mein

Khwaabon mein tujhse milta raha
chah ke mein na keh yeh saka
Ki Tere bina kya wajood mera
hona nahi kabhi tujhse juda

(Hook) (X2)
Befikar hogaya 
mai kidhar kho gaya
Ishq ki raah me            
ab tu milgaya 

[Aashna]
Mera dil meri jaaan
Mujhsee na chupaaa
Chahat karde bayaan
Mere dil ka kya? 

Jaanu mein sab kuch ,jo tu chupaye 
Mere alava sabko bataye
Pyaar se haq mujhpe jo jataye 
Na jaane kyu itna tu sataye

Meri ye dhadkane be-sabar hai
Shayad tujhko bhi na khabar hai
Mere liye tu kitna alag hai
Teri chahat ki bhi samjh hai


Khwaabon mein tujhse milti rahi
Chah ke bhi kuch keh na saki , 
Jo Aaj bhi mein tujhme hi basi
Jaana na ab tu door kahi 

(Hook) x2
Befikar ho gaya 
Mai kidhar kho gaya
Ishq ki raah me               
Ab tu mil gaya

snippet.description:
Shoutout to Kuvera! - Download the app: http://bit.ly/2Xo9Jly

India's gross domestic product or GDP contracted by a massive MINUS 23.9% in the April-June period, that is what the official NSO data said. The data revealed that majority of the sectors are hit by a negative growth after the lockdown - making this the worst economic stump in India and also the in the world amongst big economies.

However in this edition of the deshbhakt we are going to take a look at how India's GDP was anyways on a downward spiral BEFORE the virus struck - making the cut deeper for India than any other country. Even before the lockdown, GDP growth was declining since the last eight quarters.

The Finance Minister has already said that this time, the decline in growth is an ‚Äòact of God‚Äô - however data shows that an act of Fraud has been committed and this depression is not going away any time soon.

However in this edition of the deshbhakt we are going to take a look at how India's GDP was anyways on a downward spiral BEFORE the virus struck - making the cut deeper for India than any other country. Even before the lockdown, GDP growth was declining since the last eight quarters.

snippet.title: Brandy and Monica go head-to-head in Verzuz
snippet.description:
One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans ‚Äî who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

Watch Brandy and Monica's Verzuz above! #Brandy #Monica #Verzuz

snippet.title: ROCKETS at THUNDER | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | August 31, 2020
snippet.description:
ROCKETS at THUNDER | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | August 31, 2020

Led by Chris Paul‚Äôs 28 PTS, 7 REB and 3 AST, the Oklahoma City Thunder defeated the Houston Rockets, 104-100, in Game 6. Additionally for the Thunder, Danilo Gallinari added 25 PTS and 5 REB in the victory, while James Harden tallied 32 PTS, 8 REB and 7 AST for the Rockets. This best-of-seven series is now tied, 3-3.

Game 7: Wednesday, September 2 at 9:00pm/et on ESPN

snippet.title: SAOCOM 1B Mission
snippet.description:
SpaceX is targeting Sunday, August 30 at 7:18 p.m. EDT, or 23:18 UTC, for Falcon 9‚Äôs launch of the SAOCOM 1B mission, which will carry the SAOCOM 1B spacecraft to orbit in addition to two rideshare payloads, Tyvak-0172 and PlanetiQ‚Äôs GNOMES-1. The mission will lift off from Space Launch Complex 40 (SLC-40) at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station in Florida. A backup launch opportunity is available on Monday, August 31 at 7:19 p.m. EDT, or 23:19 UTC. This mission marks SpaceX‚Äôs first launch to a polar orbit from the East Coast, and the first polar launch from Florida in decades.

Falcon 9‚Äôs first stage previously launched Dragon to the International Space Station for SpaceX‚Äôs 19th and 20th commercial resupply missions, and it also supported launch of SpaceX‚Äôs ninth Starlink mission. Following stage separation, SpaceX will land Falcon 9 on Landing Zone 1 at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station. SAOCOM 1B will deploy approximately 14 minutes after launch, GNOMES-1 and Tyvak-0172 will deploy approximately 61 and 62 minutes after liftoff.

snippet.title: What if the Byzantine Empire Survived?
snippet.description:
Create your own 'What If' meme: https://bit.ly/2CH52P8  Contest is still going on!

The Eastern Romans survived for a millennia after the fall of the West before their own demise from the Ottomans. The sack of Constantinople is often thought as the end of the Medieval Age and the start of another. Politics of the past forgotten. So what if in an alternate timeline this never happened? What if the Byzantine Empire actually survived, and continued on? Here is one scenario.

snippet.title: Surviving the Hottest Place in the World
snippet.description:
Go to http://www.audible.com/yestheory or text yestheory to 500 500 to get one free audiobook, unlimited Audible originals and a 30-day free trial
New Seek Discomfort Summer Drop: https://www.seekdiscomfort.com/ live for only 72hrs!

This week after Death Valley hit the hottest temperature ever recorded... We decided to go and experience what 130F or 56C felt like... Both the best and worst idea we've ever had.

Does anyone read the description? I never really know to be honest. Well either way, this is Thomas and I'm a bit bored writing this so I'll just keep typing random things and see if anybody will notice. Conor was really upset that we kept him farting in the video so please ignore that part (or don't). Anyways, hope you liked the video we're actually pretty stoked with how it came out!

Check out Conor's channel here and tell him we sent you it'll make him very happy!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1E5Ti2P70zZxA4osS2MhiA

Thank you to Tommy, Tristan and Nathan for tagging along as our rescue team.

We have a 2nd channel! Make sure to subscribe to it here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTd7KzdwnFE3lm6LCfYDmUQ

If you want to join the Yes Fam Facebook group which is 100,000+ of our most engaged and badass community members, you can apply here: 
https://www.facebook.com/groups/yesfam/

PERFECT ROYALTY FREE MUSIC FOR YOUTUBE: free 30 day trial here: http://share.epidemicsound.com/wFFbr 

Musicbed has amazing montage and cinematic music:
http://share.mscbd.fm/YesTheory

For an amazing b-roll and footage library, checkout: http://storyblocks.com/YesTheory

Yes Theory Spotify Playlist: 
https://open.spotify.com/user/t-boogy...

Exclusive challenges on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/

Who are we? 
We believe that life can be as fulfilling as you wish, so long as you're willing to seek discomfort. And we make videos about it.

Business Inquiries: zack@yestheory.com
For community inquiries: hello@yestheory.com

https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/
https://twitter.com/yestheory
https://www.facebook.com/yestheory/
Join our texting community: +1 (323) 310-5420

Hosts: Thomas Brag, Ammar Kandil, Matt Dajer
Editors: Thomas Brag, Thomas Dajer, Cam Peddle, Bryce Perry
Produced by Lauren Rosen

snippet.title: Overhyped or AWESOME? | Vice Golf Ball Review
snippet.description:
Overhyped or AWESOME? | Vice Golf Ball Review
PGA GOLF PRO Rick Shiels tests out the Vice Pro Plus golf balls. Rick Shiels went online to pick which Vice Golf Balls would suit his game. Rick tests out the Vice Golf Ball on the golf course at Marriott Worsley Park Golf Club, tests the golf balls for spin, feel, durability, distance and much more! 

Rick Shiels is also giving away 2 dozen golf balls both on YouTube and Facebook. 

https://www.facebook.com/253446978180761/posts/1438990602959720/

‚ñ∫Become a FREE SUBSCRIBER to RICK SHIELS now 
http://bit.ly/SubRickShielsGolf

‚ñ∫ Official Apparel and footwear partner: Nike Golf 
http://www.nike.com/golf

‚ñ∫Official Garmin Ambassador: 
https://explore.garmin.com/en-GB/golf/

‚ñ∫ Hit #Subscribe & #HitTheBell so you don't miss out on any new videos! 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
‚ñ∫My Links:
Facebook  ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/RickShielsPGA/
Twitter       ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/RickShielsTwitter
Instagram ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/RickShielsIG
Web           ‚ñ∫ http://www.rickshielsgolf.co.uk/
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Hi I‚Äôm Rick Shiels, welcome to my channel RickShielsPGAGolf. This YouTube channel is designed to help you play better golf, also to help you enjoy your golf more! 

I specialise in golf club reviews, golf club unboxing, golf club news, golf club head to heads, and all about golf clubs. 

I also want to make you play better golf by providing coaching video on all topics about golf, how to fix your slice, fix your hook, help you drive the golf ball longer, hit your irons more pure, hit your irons closer to the hole and help you draw and fade your golf shots. 
I will also help you lower your score by chipping better by stopping you duff and thin chips, pitch the ball closer and also create backspin. Also I will provide you help to putt better and hole more putts! 

On this channel I also make fun and entertaining golf content based on crazy and sometimes ‚Äúgimmicky‚Äù golf clubs. I like to cut through the marketing hype about products and I like to give you the honest truth about golf equipment. 

If you enjoy the channel make sure you hit subscribe and also tap the notification bell so that you are always notified when I release a new video.

snippet.title: Brandy and Monica go head-to-head in Verzuz
snippet.description:
One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans ‚Äî who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

snippet.title: Confinement Episode 8 TRAILER!
snippet.description:

snippet.title: What if the Byzantine Empire Survived?
snippet.description:
Create your own 'What If' meme: https://bit.ly/2CH52P8  Contest is still going on!

The Eastern Romans survived for a millennia after the fall of the West before their own demise from the Ottomans. The sack of Constantinople is often thought as the end of the Medieval Age and the start of another. Politics of the past forgotten. So what if in an alternate timeline this never happened? What if the Byzantine Empire actually survived, and continued on? Here is one scenario.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/AltHistoryHub
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/AlternateHistoryHub

snippet.title: Sexual Harassment | Real Talk Season 2 Episode 4
snippet.description:
How would you know you‚Äôre being sexually harassed?

In this episode, the cast speak up about their unfortunate experience of being sexually harassed and give advice on what we should do if such a thing were to happen, not only to us, but to others as well.

If you have experienced any form of sexual harassment and are in need of help, please visit:

Sexual Assault Care Centre
http://sacc.aware.org.sg/

AWARE Singapore
https://www.aware.org.sg/

snippet.title: Christina Aguilera - Reflection (2020) (From "Mulan")
snippet.description:
Stream Disney‚Äôs Mulan September 4 exclusively on Disney+ with Premier Access. Additional fee required. More info: http://disneyplus.com/mulan

‚ÄúReflection‚Äù
Performed by Christina Aguilera (@xtina) From Mulan (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) Download/stream it here: https://disneymusic.co/Mulan?iqid=dmvevo ‚öî 

‚öî ‚öî When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Army to defend the country from Northern invaders, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. Masquerading as a man, Hua Jun, she is tested every step of the way and must harness her inner-strength and embrace her true potential. It is an epic journey that will transform her into an honored warrior and earn her the respect of a grateful nation‚Ä¶and a proud father. ‚ÄúMulan‚Äù features a celebrated international cast that includes: Yifei Liu as Mulan; Donnie Yen as Commander Tung; Jason Scott Lee as B√∂ri Khan; Yoson An as Cheng Honghui; with Gong Li as Xianniang and Jet Li as the Emperor. The film is directed by Niki Caro from a screenplay by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver and Elizabeth Martin & Lauren Hynek based on the narrative poem ‚ÄúThe Ballad of Mulan.‚Äù

Dipandu oleh Andhika Pratama, Raffi Ahmad dan Yuki Kato.

Follow media sosial SCTV lainnya!

Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/SCTV
Twitter : https://twitter.com/SCTV

snippet.title: The Batman - DC FanDome Teaser
snippet.description:
Robert Pattinson is #TheBatman.

https://www.instagram.com/thebatman/
https://www.facebook.com/thebatman
https://twitter.com/thebatman
http://thebatman.com

From Warner Bros. Pictures comes ‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù with director Matt Reeves (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) at the helm and with Robert Pattinson (‚ÄúTenet,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lighthouse,‚Äù ‚ÄúGood Time‚Äù) starring as Gotham City‚Äôs vigilante detective, Batman, and billionaire Bruce Wayne.

Also in the star-studded ensemble as Gotham‚Äôs famous and infamous cast of characters are Zo√´ Kravitz (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) as Selina Kyle; Paul Dano (‚ÄúLove & Mercy,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù) as Edward Nashton; Jeffrey Wright (the ‚ÄúHunger Games‚Äù films) as the GCPD‚Äôs James Gordon; John Turturro (the ‚ÄúTransformers‚Äù films) as Carmine Falcone; Peter Sarsgaard (‚ÄúThe Magnificent Seven,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlack Mass‚Äù) as Gotham D.A. Gil Colson; Barry Keoghan (‚ÄúDunkirk‚Äù) as Officer Stanley Merkel; Jayme Lawson (‚ÄúFarewell Amor‚Äù) as mayoral candidate Bella Re√°l; with Andy Serkis (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films, ‚ÄúBlack Panther‚Äù) as Alfred; and Colin Farrell (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,‚Äù ‚ÄúDumbo‚Äù) as Oswald Cobblepot.

‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù was written by Matt Reeves & Peter Craig.  Reeves and Dylan Clark (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) are producing the film, with Simon Emanuel, Michael E. Uslan, Walter Hamada and Chantal Nong Vo serving as executive producers.  Reeves‚Äô behind-the-scenes creative team includes Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (‚ÄúLion,‚Äù upcoming ‚ÄúDune‚Äù); his ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù production designer, James Chinlund; editors William Hoy (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) and Tyler Nelson (‚ÄúRememory‚Äù); Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book‚Äù); Oscar-nominated SFX supervisor Dominic Tuohy (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù); Oscar-nominated sound mixer Stuart Wilson (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù) and costume designers Glyn Dillon (the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise) and David Crossman (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); hair designer Zoe Tahir (upcoming ‚ÄúNo Time to Die,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpectre‚Äù); and Oscar-nominated makeup designer Naomi Donne (‚Äú1917‚Äù).

Based on characters from DC.  Batman was created by Bob Kane with Bill Finger.  ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù is set to open in theaters October 1, 2021 in select 3D and 2D and IMAX theaters and will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

snippet.title: BEST FRIEND KO NOON, STEPMOM KO NGAYON!
snippet.description:
MAHALAGANG PAALALA:


Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.


Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.


Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 10M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.


Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

snippet.description: Led by Chris Paul‚Äôs 28 points (15 in the 4th quarter), 7 rebounds and 3 assists, the Thunder defeated the Rockets, 104-100, in Game 6. snippet.title: Israel Adesanya, Paulo Costa get HEATED in interview before UFC 253 fight | SportsCenter
snippet.description:
UFC middleweight champion Israel Adesanya and Paulo Costa chat with Michael Eaves on SportsCenter weeks before their scheduled fight at UFC 253. Both fighters discuss their preparations in the time of COVID-19, how it has affected their families and if their schedules are getting changed at all. They then get heated, calling each other "weak," "dumb" and much more.

snippet.title: Die Abschleppbr√ºder vom Autobahnkreuz | die nordreportage | NDR Doku
snippet.description:
Die Br√ºder Oliver und Rouven Fl√∂rke sind Abschleppunternehmer, 24 Stunden erreichbar und am Lehrter Kreuz zwischen der A2 und A7 unterwegs, zwei der meistbefahrenen Autobahnen in Deutschland. Die beiden leiten seit einem Jahr gemeinsam das Familienunternehmen mit 20 Mitarbeitenden. Doch der Seniorchef, ihr Vater, kann sich immer noch nicht so ganz trennen.
